node.text:
What makes you feel most at home? For couple Alyssa, Sam and their little girl Avery, it means being together. 🏠🤍 This #Pride month and beyond, everyone should experience the acceptance of home. #HomeIsForEveryone is our initiative to share messages of hope and create safe spaces for the LGBTQIA+ community, in partnership with @itgetsbetter. 🏳️‍🌈
“Home is a feeling. What better feeling to have than being accepted & valued by the people closest to us?”
#PrideMonth #Pride2021 #ItGetsBetter #CrateandBarrel

Like this post & we’ll donate. We’re obsessed with this young activist’s bedroom makeover and Q&A. 😍 @genesisbutler_ is an advocate for animal rights, and one of the youngest people to ever give a TEDx talk (#nbd). An ethical vegan since she was 6—she started @genesisforanimals, which provides funding to sanctuaries and rescues that provide animals with a permanent home. For each like this post gets, we will donate $3 toward Genesis’ causes (full donation amount up to $1500). Funding will go towards the care of animals including food, shelter, transportation costs, surgeries, and vet visits. Charity contact information: genesisforanimals@yahoo.org. Runs from 4/23 - 4/30.
